{"tid":931411,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔都是有故事的人🧣","createTime":"2018-12-07T04:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T05:16:51.000Z","uid":111768,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"60f34301ae728f5d526a9dae9a3ec07ff486b9bf","tid":931411,"uid":111768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T04:29:21.000Z","msg":"以前上親連登都望到啲post不斷有留言：<br />\n女人係雞；女人味到80歲之前都唔好比飽飯食諸如此類<br />\n<br />\n以前就會覺得係講笑同埋講呢啲嘢好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但而家睇返 就會覺得連登仔都是一群<span style=\"color: red;\">被</span>拋棄的人<br />\n而呢種拋棄卻源自於自身本深情，奈何她人情淺<br />\n<br />\n所以各位巴打，有帽要及時除，世界太複雜，唔好再交個心出黎俾人握住，因為佢可以隨時渣爆你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後祝願連登各位巴打陌路人步步順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29e4d4ef5f2dd7f0770e0c8cc9b038174856e76","tid":931411,"uid":24596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T05:16:51.000Z","msg":"半認真<br />\n背後真係有啲道理喺入邊<br />\n不過，這裡是㜕登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}